text: José Mário Vaz (born 10 December 1957) is a Guinea-Bissauan politician. He was the President of Guinea-Bissau, from 23 June 2014 to 27 February 2020. == References == Category:1957 births Category:Presidents of Guinea-Bissau Category:Government ministers Category:Mayors Category:Roman Catholics Category:Living people
